parameters: \nc<>...I mean, what's the point of thinking about that?

\nc<>Even just a little while ago, if I had let my guard down
even for a moment, I wouldn't have been able to refuse.

\nc<>Help me, Levantia! A villain appeared in the downtown area,
meow!

\nc<>That's right. Even in this situation, we have to protect
the citizens...
